                     <interp inst="t18311020-226-person1510" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live with my father, in Calmell-buildings. I was in the buildings, and the prisoner came and said he had a cap, which he put into his pocket; he then gave it me to mind for him - I took it to Mrs. Sarsfield, and left it with her; the prisoner afterwards asked me for it, and I took him to Sarsfield's - she asked him the price of it; he said 2s., and she bought it for 1s. 6d.</p>
